OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy across Scotland
OL,6,Fand Northern Ireland with some patchy
OL,7,Frain. Otherwise, early mist, fog and
OL,8,Flow cloud gradually clearing leaving a
OL,9,Ffine day with sunny spells. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarmer than Tuesday, especially in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy across
OL,14,FScotland and Northern Ireland, with
OL,15,Frain becoming more persistent
OL,16,Flater.Dry elsewhere, with some patchy
OL,17,Flow cloud and hill fog developing. A
OL,18,Fmilder night for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
