OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FRain across the northwest
OL,6,Fmaking slow progress southeastwards
OL,7,Fduring Thursday. Much of England and
OL,8,FWales though remaining dry with
OL,9,Fsunniest skies in the east. Feeling
OL,10,Fwarm away from the northwest.
